N2  - The article announces that Edward J. Conlon was selected for two editorial positions at ?Academy of Management Review.? Conlon is the University of Notre Dame's Edward Frederick Sorin Society Professor of Management. His appointment to Incoming Editor is effective July 1, 1999 and he will become Editor in December. Conlon's teaching career includes the 1997 Presidential Award. He was a consulting editor for ?Journal of Applied Psychology.?
